---
title: American-Spiced Chicken & Mustard Mash with BBQ Gravy & Creamy Slaw
description: We have a stellar lineup of flavours tonight. Take a bite of seared chicken seasoned in our All-American spice, it’s warming aromas will make your mouth water. Next try out the potato mash, it’s not only soft but has a sharp and delicious mustard stirred through. Finally a smokey BBQ gravy to pour over, it's the perfect finishing touch.
